      ]
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "\"P\" POSITION."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Park."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "The synchroniser sleeve remains at the reverse position. The park rod and cam engage the park pawl with the park gear. The output shaft is mechanically locked.",
